</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_113" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_113_r2l31"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> ~ Rüdenhauſer vnd der ~ Popp / ſein beſtalt cʒu ſlahen / cʒu der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r2l32">Freÿenſtat / So iſt der ~ höppfell / vnd ſein ſune beſtalt cʒu lauff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_113_r2l33">cʒu ſlahen / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_113" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> Rüdenhauser und der Popp sein bestalt czu
                        slahen czu der Freyenstat; so ist der Höppfell und sein sune bestalt czu
                        Lauff czu slahen.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
